    public ResponseEntity<ConvertedDatatablesData<Address>> CitiesItemAddressesThymeleafController.datatablesByIdsIn(@RequestParam("ids") List<Long> ids, DatatablesColumns datatablesColumns, GlobalSearch search, DatatablesPageable pageable, @RequestParam("draw") Integer draw) {
        
        Page<Address> addresses = getAddressService().findAllByIdsIn(ids, search, pageable);
        long totalAddressesCount = addresses.getTotalElements();
        ConvertedDatatablesData<Address> data =  new ConvertedDatatablesData<Address>(addresses, totalAddressesCount, draw, getConversionService(), datatablesColumns);
        return ResponseEntity.ok(data);
    }
    
